txt.en: Banner posts can be found along the Rammas.\n\nYou should place banners of Gondor on top of the Rammas.
'Plant some banners of Gondor along the Out-wall. After we've retaken the Rammas, the enemy will be reminded of their defeat!'
Banner posts can be found along the Rammas.\n\nYou should place banners of Gondor on top of the Rammas.
Easterlings have invaded the northern Rammas and it is up to you to see them off the Out-wall.
